Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.03,0:03:28.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是夏日節
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.17,0:03:37.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各種樂隊在寬敞的野外會場進行演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.11,0:03:40.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會有幾萬人聚集在一起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.48,0:03:43.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前就想去一次夏日節了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.69,0:03:44.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.93,0:03:48.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去聽職業樂隊的演奏也能增加經驗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.98,0:03:50.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就這樣定了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.96,0:03:52.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏日節是在山裡舉行的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.84,0:03:54.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會場是在山裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.01,0:03:56.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.60,0:04:09.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會被吃掉吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.10,0:04:11.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我不知道你在想什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.91,0:04:13.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但肯定不是你想的那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.52,0:04:15.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但票要怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.71,0:04:16.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還能弄到手嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.27,0:04:18.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.43,0:04:19.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你們沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.98,0:04:21.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次是特別服務哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.46,0:04:23.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.48,0:04:24.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是小佐和
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.42,0:04:27.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說  你真是神出鬼沒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.56,0:04:29.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能給我來杯麥茶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.63,0:04:30.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.80,0:04:33.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次參加夏日節啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.03,0:04:36.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是第一次參加野外演唱會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.61,0:04:38.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定很棒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.39,0:04:40.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以這麼悠閒的心態去的話會輸的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.27,0:04:42.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輸給什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.50,0:04:43.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輸給夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.35,0:04:43.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了  
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.23,0:04:47.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炙熱耀眼的太陽  令人悶絕的熱氣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.47,0:04:50.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有此時守候著獵物的夏蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.97,0:04:54.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參加夏日節的人  要和這一切戰鬥到底
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.80,0:04:55.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.21,0:04:56.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.05,0:04:57.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.91,0:04:59.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪學姐很有幹勁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.34,0:05:12.09,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（臨時區間公車站）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.81,0:05:19.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  還沒人來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.84,0:05:21.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.94,0:05:23.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.85,0:05:24.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.22,0:05:27.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  只有小梓一個人？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.58,0:05:28.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.25,0:05:29.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.18,0:05:34.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然按時來的就只有紬和梓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.73,0:05:37.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪學姐沒睡好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.76,0:05:40.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整晚都在挑選要聽哪個樂隊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.14,0:05:43.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全是想看的樂隊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.58,0:05:46.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會場好像也有好幾個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.81,0:05:50.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴士已經來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.47,0:05:52.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打電話給唯學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.73,0:05:55.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在這裡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.96,0:05:56.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.64,0:05:57.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.90,0:05:57.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.34,0:06:00.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在的話就說一聲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.98,0:06:04.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀～我想看看你們什麼時候才會注意到我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.30,0:06:08.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我從沒想過唯學姐會先到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.58,0:06:11.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  還有一個人沒來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.80,0:06:15.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.48,0:06:18.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佐和  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.82,0:06:22.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天晚上去了演唱會  然後一直喝到早上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.83,0:06:24.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒睡就直接過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.67,0:06:29.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師  很冷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.40,0:06:33.51,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼明知今天要出發還做那種事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.06,0:06:34.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.87,0:06:35.18,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明自己說了要鼓足幹勁的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.06,0:06:41.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暈車了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.60,0:06:43.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們很合得來嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.03,0:06:46.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佐和是宿醉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.61,0:06:48.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是ROCK派啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.61,0:06:50.92,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（On the rock：對酒精濃度較高的酒的一種狂熱飲法，\N常直接稱為rock，在rocks glass等中只加入冰後飲用。）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.24,0:06:50.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思  我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.28,0:06:52.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.51,0:06:54.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯學姐很不適合坐車啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.30,0:06:57.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個樂隊和這個樂隊一定要看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.77,0:06:58.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒可能啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.81,0:07:01.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間相同卻在不同會場嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.46,0:07:02.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要兩個身體
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.73,0:07:04.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩選一
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.09,0:07:07.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者每個聽一半
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.24,0:07:08.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想瞬間移動
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.46,0:07:09.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.53,0:07:11.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪學姐在說任性的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.93,0:07:14.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要吃炒麵  炒麵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.31,0:07:16.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要吃炒麵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.56,0:07:18.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紬學姐也在說小規模任性的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.77,0:07:18.49,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不好嘛  律
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.95,0:07:19.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.41,0:07:23.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可能不行了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.96,0:07:30.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從早到晚都能聽到演奏…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.68,0:07:32.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情緒一直很高漲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.94,0:07:34.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然高漲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.20,0:07:36.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  在吃冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.89,0:07:38.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很多好吃的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.80,0:07:40.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有土特產賣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.29,0:07:42.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害  路邊餐館裡什麼都有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.18,0:07:45.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是不舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.35,0:07:46.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.83,0:07:48.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵也來嘗嘗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.68,0:07:51.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高原特濃牛奶軟冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.64,0:07:53.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.74,0:07:59.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息時間快要結束了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.72,0:08:02.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  我還沒買土特產呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.54,0:08:04.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡又不是目的地啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.93,0:08:07.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  在這裡吃不到炒麵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.42,0:08:11.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紬學姐也微妙地脫線了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.18,0:08:16.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.46,0:08:19.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯…這樣很危險…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.62,0:08:21.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能趕上開幕式吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.52,0:08:22.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.06,0:08:25.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會場裡也有好吃的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.63,0:08:28.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  能完全沉浸在音樂中的兩天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.47,0:08:31.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯  炒麵  我們去吃炒麵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.36,0:08:32.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之盡情地去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.36,0:08:33.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合宿真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.49,0:08:33.97,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  鼓足幹勁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.14,0:08:36.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脫線成這樣沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.85,0:08:40.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要大聲說話…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.44,0:08:49.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有…  好多…  人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.89,0:08:51.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經有這麼多人了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.93,0:08:53.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧  在開始之前就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.40,0:08:56.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.44,0:08:58.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡有三億人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.45,0:09:00.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就超過日本的總人口了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.01,0:09:01.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  各位
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.08,0:09:02.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.69,0:09:04.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠閒模式到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.60,0:09:06.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佐和是最悠閒的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.05,0:09:09.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說  你不是因為宿醉而精疲力盡了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.55,0:09:11.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經把昨天的我給拋棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.98,0:09:15.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是會場的入口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.46,0:09:17.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這以後就是戰場
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.49,0:09:18.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太誇張了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.40,0:09:24.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才用票換的腕套是進入搖滾祭典的通行證
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.99,0:09:27.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄丟的話就不能再入場了  要小心保護好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.98,0:09:31.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  在進去之前先去野營區
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.16,0:09:33.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須要確保今晚睡的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.89,0:09:37.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了  來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.38,0:09:39.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平坦的地方已經沒位置了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.82,0:09:42.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法了  就在斜坡上忍耐一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.17,0:09:46.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  這樣睡覺的時候不會腦充血嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.97,0:09:48.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭朝上不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.50,0:09:54.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很熟練啊  小佐和
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.55,0:09:56.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  把行李都放進去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.53,0:10:02.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紬紬？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.99,0:10:04.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀呵～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.86,0:10:08.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有點悶熱  但感覺很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.60,0:10:10.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是背後好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.07,0:10:12.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.52,0:10:15.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必需品都拿著了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.61,0:10:16.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.41,0:10:17.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防曬霜塗了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.06,0:10:18.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.14,0:10:20.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝的東西買了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.62,0:10:21.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.15,0:10:24.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中暑對策很完美
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.35,0:10:25.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.45,0:10:26.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去買運動飲料
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.97,0:10:28.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這個不要了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.42,0:10:29.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也帶著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.66,0:10:32.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以洗手  或在熱的時候往身上澆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.41,0:10:33.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水一定會幫上忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.59,0:10:36.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣喜歡指揮的人還真存在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.46,0:10:38.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不是運動鞋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.22,0:10:41.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒帶別的鞋來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.73,0:10:44.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  把我的沙灘拖鞋借給你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.87,0:10:47.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為能在河邊玩就帶來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.61,0:10:49.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是來幹什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.14,0:10:51.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯  謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.75,0:10:52.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用謝～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.44,0:10:55.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  驅蟲劑塗了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.02,0:11:01.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在來噴驅蟲劑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.30,0:11:01.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.02,0:11:03.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紬紬  謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.88,0:11:05.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  小澪也來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.63,0:11:08.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓人想起小學時的郊遊了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.56,0:11:11.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那接下來我來幫紬紬噴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.20,0:11:14.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己能噴  沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.57,0:11:18.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  我也想噴噴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.20,0:11:19.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.84,0:11:21.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…真像小學生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.97,0:11:24.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會幫小律和梓喵噴的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.42,0:11:26.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們要噴到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.87,0:11:28.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佐和什麼時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.43,0:11:29.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  要進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.83,0:11:34.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請進
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.99,0:11:37.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請為零垃圾運動出份力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.08,0:11:38.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡配發垃圾袋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.69,0:11:40.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.31,0:11:42.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要開始了  夏日節
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.31,0:11:48.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,K-ON!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.01,0:11:55.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我來進行會場內的說明
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.60,0:11:56.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.54,0:11:58.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fsp150}　{\fsp1}Fire Stage{\r}\N首先是主打的烈火舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.72,0:12:02.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是能收納約4萬人的主會場之一
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.37,0:12:05.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,場地呈平緩斜坡  所以後面也很容易觀看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.06,0:12:08.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fsp250}　{\fsp1}Thunder Stage{\r}\N這裡是被稱為裡主場的雷霆舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.96,0:12:10.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以收納1萬人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.75,0:12:15.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並有很多專業方向的樂隊來演出
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.53,0:12:18.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會經常往返這兩個舞台吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.71,0:12:21.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  距離大概約700米
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.44,0:12:25.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算10秒跑完100米  也要花將近70秒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.30,0:12:26.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你放鬆點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.41,0:12:30.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有年輕樂隊多出沒的室內舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.82,0:12:34.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最裡面的是爵士樂隊和奇怪樂隊較多的舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.73,0:12:38.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有木吉他音樂人較多出沒的小舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.71,0:12:40.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就是音樂盛典
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.10,0:12:43.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飯  飯在哪兒有賣？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.58,0:12:45.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯  我要吃炒麵哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.53,0:12:49.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得這兩個人哪裡脫線了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.70,0:12:50.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.72,0:12:51.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.65,0:12:54.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過話說回來  還真虧小佐和有票呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.83,0:12:56.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個節日我每年都有來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.33,0:12:58.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可為什麼會有6張？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.52,0:13:03.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來預定一起來的朋友突然取消了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.34,0:13:05.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佐和被討厭了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.83,0:13:08.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒那回事啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.60,0:13:12.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…大概
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.93,0:13:14.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你讓我們情何以堪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.65,0:13:24.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪  沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.74,0:13:26.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  實際來了才發現
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.22,0:13:28.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又熱  人又多…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.13,0:13:31.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.93,0:13:35.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.29,0:13:40.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK  讓我們燃起來吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.42,0:13:46.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.45,0:13:47.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聲音好大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.98,0:13:53.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是夏日節
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.67,0:13:56.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.36,0:14:01.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏日節！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.70,0:14:02.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢！  
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.63,0:14:06.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  小澪的初次夏日節
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.87,0:14:08.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這支樂隊感覺不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.25,0:14:13.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  主唱的聲音夠滄桑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.34,0:14:16.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  大家  準備移動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.69,0:14:17.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.46,0:14:19.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還想多聽一下這支樂隊啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.87,0:14:22.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最想推薦的樂隊在室內舞台啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.35,0:14:25.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微有點遠  我們要衝過去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.86,0:14:28.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  老師你就一個人去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.85,0:14:30.83,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  那我可去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.85,0:14:32.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律  律  我也想去雷霆舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.58,0:14:33.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.26,0:14:35.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快！再不快點的話就要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.55,0:14:37.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們留在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.77,0:14:38.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.17,0:14:41.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  那我去去就回
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.39,0:14:44.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一會兒再聯繫集合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.98,0:14:46.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快趕快！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.29,0:14:47.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.66,0:14:48.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那回頭見
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.28,0:14:50.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.33,0:14:52.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.33,0:14:55.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  梓喵也想再聽下這個樂隊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.14,0:14:57.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紬學姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.45,0:15:00.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我穿著沙灘拖鞋跑不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.93,0:15:06.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們闊別三年再次回到這夏日搖滾的舞台來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.74,0:15:06.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律  律
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.04,0:15:07.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.32,0:15:10.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個樂隊的吉他手是左撇子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.27,0:15:11.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.03,0:15:16.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然左手感覺很奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.86,0:15:18.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然這話由我來說有點不太妥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.88,0:15:21.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到夥伴很高興我也懂啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.58,0:15:22.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微消停點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.53,0:15:28.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯學姐在認真地看著表演
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.48,0:15:33.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果受到感染後能更加更加認真練習的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.60,0:15:37.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵  我有事想問一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.36,0:15:38.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  什麼事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.00,0:15:43.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個貝司手的髮型是怎麼弄出來的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.30,0:15:45.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是天然卷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.20,0:15:47.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連紬學姐也…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.05,0:15:55.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超人氣…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.29,0:15:57.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  我們一起來排
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.30,0:15:58.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.76,0:15:59.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.92,0:16:03.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起！還剩10份完售！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.97,0:16:04.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.88,0:16:08.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紬…紬學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.30,0:16:10.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作點  不可以屈服啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.65,0:16:12.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.99,0:16:15.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們去買小唯想吃的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.79,0:16:16.30,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（海員沙司批薩）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.92,0:16:17.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.17,0:16:21.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭啦  我要回去～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.73,0:16:23.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別撒嬌啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.33,0:16:25.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  郵件
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.51,0:16:26.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作得好快！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.78,0:16:28.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小律發來的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.15,0:16:30.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,14點烈火舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.17,0:16:32.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,15點雷霆舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.14,0:16:35.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,16點再回烈火舞台…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.68,0:16:36.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好困難啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.31,0:16:38.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  我跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.09,0:16:43.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紬學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.09,0:16:42.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紬紬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.24,0:16:50.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  爽歪啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.46,0:17:07.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank You！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.54,0:17:17.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨變小了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.16,0:17:20.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到下一個想看的樂隊出演還蠻久的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.44,0:17:22.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子不餓嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.84,0:17:24.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午飯沒吃成啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.91,0:17:27.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是吃了可麗餅和冰淇淋嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.83,0:17:29.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…那不是飯啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.13,0:17:32.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去買晚飯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.90,0:17:34.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.70,0:17:35.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.26,0:17:38.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你們佔位子了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.30,0:17:41.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  木板道的中間不是有條小河嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.52,0:17:43.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在那兒等你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.03,0:17:48.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之就先鋪在這兒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.09,0:17:49.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.54,0:17:53.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跳～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.66,0:17:55.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  小澪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.83,0:17:57.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.20,0:17:59.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.85,0:18:00.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊有賣T恤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.00,0:18:03.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那個左手彈吉他的樂隊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.29,0:18:07.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飯呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.46,0:18:09.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿上試試
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.58,0:18:13.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯啊  我也有點想要了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.39,0:18:14.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起買吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.75,0:18:16.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.67,0:18:18.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.34,0:18:19.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.05,0:18:22.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  小佐和發來的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.52,0:18:24.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說她買了章魚燒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.81,0:18:26.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一會兒帶過來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.30,0:18:27.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,章魚燒～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.25,0:18:35.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好清爽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.59,0:18:37.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還可以洗澡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.40,0:18:38.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.92,0:18:40.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我渾身痛痛的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.09,0:18:43.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓今年也是一身黑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.48,0:18:46.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然擦了防曬霜  但沒有效果
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.25,0:18:48.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可愛不就行了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.63,0:18:51.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我回去睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.69,0:18:52.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  這就睡？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.23,0:18:55.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搖頭舞過頭了  脖子疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.02,0:18:59.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…是不是認為我上年紀了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.16,0:19:00.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒有完全沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.48,0:19:22.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.98,0:19:25.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  梓喵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.78,0:19:27.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在這裡做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.62,0:19:31.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在聽遠處傳來的音樂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.10,0:19:34.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的一整晚都在演奏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.80,0:19:39.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  請就坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.84,0:19:40.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.60,0:19:45.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐著不動不會被蚊子咬嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.22,0:19:47.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.34,0:19:49.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帶著兩個防蟲帶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.74,0:19:50.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.24,0:19:52.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你一個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.13,0:19:54.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.09,0:19:56.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  你們兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.75,0:19:58.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡談悄悄話？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.84,0:19:59.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家也過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.16,0:20:01.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐在這裡聽音樂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.76,0:20:10.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得像夢一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.75,0:20:12.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  很不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.87,0:20:17.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這麼廣闊的地方  一直演奏著音樂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.03,0:20:22.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天看到的樂隊都很帥氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.78,0:20:27.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  聲音的氣勢…或者說魄力真是十足呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.56,0:20:35.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  還是我們的演奏更棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.56,0:20:39.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面對專業人士你那是哪門子自信？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.01,0:20:40.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.77,0:20:45.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說這話前  先學會不彈錯吉他吧我說！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.02,0:20:48.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…一針見血啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.95,0:20:53.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  還是我們的演奏更棒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.17,0:20:57.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整體感啦  怎麼說好呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.74,0:21:00.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  是氣場！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.78,0:21:06.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你懂什麼叫氣場嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.25,0:21:08.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不懂～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.47,0:21:10.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.07,0:21:14.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「放學後茶會」是個很好的樂隊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.96,0:21:15.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.83,0:21:16.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  唯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.24,0:21:18.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是  小澪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.98,0:21:22.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯！就算是專業人士我們也不會落後的！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.05,0:21:23.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連梓也…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.05,0:21:25.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次不是作為聽眾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.76,0:21:27.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要作為演奏者參加夏日節
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.17,0:21:29.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…這麼起勁？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.69,0:21:30.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.08,0:21:32.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.45,0:21:36.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.91,0:21:39.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能在這裡演出可就太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.73,0:21:40.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.62,0:21:53.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後我們也能一直組樂隊就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.96,0:21:55.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.70,0:21:57.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.45,0:21:59.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.56,0:22:04.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  就這樣  直到永遠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.69,0:23:47.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡吃炒麵味道真好啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.27,0:23:48.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  確實確實
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.08,0:23:52.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  夏日節的時候紬學姐也非常期待
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.22,0:23:55.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但最後因為賣完了而沒吃到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.46,0:23:58.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有別墅哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.25,0:24:01.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能去芬蘭哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.49,0:24:03.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帶你們去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.87,0:24:05.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你誰啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.86,0:24:06.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.50,0:24:09.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現剩下的午飯～


